snippet.title: Vectrexagon for the Vectrex By Andreas Gustafsson (SDW)
snippet.description:
Vectrexagon Game play video.

Vectrexagon 
By Andreas Gustafsson (SDW) 
SDW Developments 
2015
Pictures from 2016-03-14  package delivery. 
Vectrexagon for the Vectrex / 光速船 / Kousokusen 1982 - 1984 home arcade vector graphics based video game system. 

http://www.sdwdevelopments.com

http://www.sdwdevelopments.com/vectrexagon.html

https://www.packratvg.com/vvgon.html

http://www.ag1976.com/

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KPniWxXBZ_k&ab_channel=vectrexer

Vectrexagon game cartridge delivery pictures from 2016-03-14.
https://goo.gl/photos/BBrezrbc2fLERtmy5

Earlier Vectrexagon Alpha software build video from 2013.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AQrneT0pijU&ab_channel=AndreasGustafsson
